even buy books!

20
00:02:19,935 --> 00:02:23,234
Finished, Crivelli?
"Compañera" Falcone has the floor.

21
00:02:24,973 --> 00:02:28,967
Let's not be naive!
This dialogue is just another delay.

22
00:02:29,579 --> 00:02:30,944
