tomorrow or not.

31
00:03:00,042 --> 00:03:03,978
Not all of us at Fine Arts
think that!

32
00:03:04,647 --> 00:03:06,205
Shut up, you nerd!

33
00:03:06,449 --> 00:03:09,849
The question is, will there
be police repression?

34
00:03:10,952 --> 00:03:14,489
Probably... and infiltrates, too.

35
00:03:14,489 --> 00:03:20,052
In that case, we could ask
the guerrilla for protection.

36
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:23,827
- No way!
- Bullshit!

37
00:03:25,066 --> 00:03:26,658
Order, order!

38
00:03:27,769 --> 00:03:29,601
Not a bad idea!

39
00:03:29,705 --> 00:03:31,900
- Right!
- Yes, that's right!

40
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:37,207
Silence!

41
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:40,072
Silence!

42
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:45,847
Please, think before you speak.

43
00:03:46,821 --> 00:03:51,019
