- After you, sir.
- Please, doctor.

80
00:09:30,630 --> 00:09:32,860
After you, engineer.

81
00:09:43,477 --> 00:09:45,240
Look... Claudia Falcone.

82
00:09:45,645 --> 00:09:48,739
She's lost her head for you.

83
00:09:49,449 --> 00:09:52,350
Claudia, give him a chance.

84
00:09:52,586 --> 00:09:54,713
Tell her you love her.

85
00:09:56,256 --> 00:09:59,248
Is she dating a Fine Arts student?

86
00:09:59,826 --> 00:10:02,454
I know everything about Claudia,

87
00:10:03,497 --> 00:10:05,555
but I'm no rat.

88
00:10:05,798 --> 00:10:08,631
Oh, yeah?
Get off it.

89
00:10:09,536 --> 00:10:11,561
We couldn't hand
in the petition...

90
00:10:12,406 --> 00:10:15,341
butwe proved we aren'tweak.

91
00:10:26,019 --> 00:10:28,579
My poor baby!

92
00:10:29,322 --> 00:10:31,552
Stop it!
It hurts when I laugh.

93
00:10:35,628 --> 00:10:37,220
Boy, did they get you!

94
00:10:37,997 --> 00:10:42,059
Tell the others it was
worthwhile, anyhow.

95
00:10:42,169 --> 00:10:45,366
We know the matter is being
carefully reviewed.

96
00:10:45,672 --> 00:10:48,800
Sure, we'll have our pass.

97
00:11:08,961 --> 00:11:10,861
Pablo, what are you doing here?

98
