Nothing... justwalking.
And you?

99
00:11:13,867 --> 00:11:16,665
- Me? School's finished.
- Sure.

100
00:11:17,537 --> 00:11:19,368
- You're...
- What?

101
00:11:19,439 --> 00:11:21,134
Got something to do?

102
00:11:21,608 --> 00:11:24,008
- Nothing.
- Fine. Let's go.

103
00:11:36,255 --> 00:11:38,883
<i>Tucumán,
in the operational zone...</i>

104
00:11:38,958 --> 00:11:42,486
<i>six non-identified guerrilla
were killed by the Army...</i>

105
00:11:42,562 --> 00:11:45,030
<i>in two clashes.</i>

106
00:11:45,198 --> 00:11:46,961
<i>La Plata, Government House.</i>

107
00:11:47,134 --> 00:11:49,102
<i>Any news on the pass?</i>

108
00:11:49,169 --> 00:11:51,399
<i>You must be patient.</i>

109
00:11:51,838 --> 00:11:53,169
<i>There's a rumor.</i>

110
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:56,766
<i>Once again. It's being
carefully reviewed.</i>

111
00:11:57,209 --> 00:11:58,335
<i>Mendoza...</i>

112
00:11:59,245 --> 00:12:02,009
Bullshit!
They're fobbing us off again.

113
00:12:02,982 --> 00:12:05,450
- We'll have to wait.
- How long?

114
00:12:05,885 --> 00:12:07,580
Afew days.

115
00:12:07,853 --> 00:12:10,515
If there's no answer
we'll demonstrate again.

116
00:12:15,529 --> 00:12:20,228
In politics,
one must be patient.

117
00:12:20,333 --> 00:12:23,325
Sure, Dad.
Where did patience get you?

118
00:12:23,769 --> 00:12:25,396
Leave her alone, Dad.

119
00:12:25,471 --> 00:12:26,529
That I don't know...

120
00:12:27,206 --> 00:12:29,606
but I do know one thing.

121
00:12:30,142 --> 00:12:33,202
In politics, nothing is free.

122
00:12:34,513 --> 00:12:38,415
Make sure you don't pay
a high price.

123
00:12:38,617 --> 00:12:41,552
C'mon... stop arguing.

124
00:12:43,355 --> 00:12:45,654
- Don't annoy your father.
- Ok, Mom.

125
00:12:46,092 --> 00:12:48,617
<i>La Plata...
A Law School professor...</i>

126
00:12:48,695 --> 00:12:50,560
<i>has been reported missing...</i>

127
00:12:50,630 --> 00:12:54,793
<i>while two of this students
were kidnapped yesterday.</i>

128
00:13:00,506 --> 00:13:04,704
- Perhaps your dad's right.
- How would you know?

129
00:13:05,144 --> 00:13:09,046
- Let him speak.
- He's a traitor!

130
00:13:09,782 --> 00:13:12,216
You were a Peronist,
weren't you?

131
00:13:12,451 --> 00:13:13,748
Perón is dead.

132
00:13:13,852 --> 00:13:16,447
And now it's
the Che Guevara Youth.

133
00:13:16,590 --> 00:13:19,922
- Che is also dead.
- That's different. He...

134
00:13:19,992 --> 00:13:21,926
Perón's dead,
but the people are his heir.

135
00:13:22,127 --> 00:13:24,459
What people?
Isabelita Perón?

136
00:13:24,530 --> 00:13:28,296
No. We, the youth.

137
00:13:32,204 --> 00:13:34,968
Hi, Pablo.
Up so early?

138
00:13:35,374 --> 00:13:37,239
- Is Horacio home?
- Sure, come on in.

139
00:13:41,513 --> 00:13:43,777
Wake up, listen.

140
00:13:45,685 --> 00:13:48,084
"To protect
the students' interests...

141
00:13:48,187 --> 00:13:51,281
a cheaper bus fare
has been granted."

142
00:13:52,524 --> 00:13:53,786
The pass!

143
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,225
- No!
- Yes!

144
00:14:07,106 --> 00:14:11,873
<i>Hand in hand,
with all our might,</i>

145
00:14:11,944 --> 00:14:15,174
<i>we got the pass all right!</i>

146
00:14:51,517 --> 00:14:52,950
What about me?

147
00:15:23,315 --> 00:15:25,476
- I won't be back for lunch.
- OK.

148
00:15:25,684 --> 00:15:27,083
One less.

149
00:15:51,009 --> 00:15:53,375
- Good morning.
- How are you?

150
00:15:57,716 --> 00:15:58,944
Hello.

151
00:15:59,385 --> 00:16:01,546
Pablito, I wasn't expecting you.

152
00:16:01,987 --> 00:16:03,352
I finally came.

153
00:16:07,892 --> 00:16:09,359
Thanks.

154
00:16:09,994 --> 00:16:12,224
- Is your sister in?
- Out shopping.

155
00:16:13,131 --> 00:16:15,895
Give her this, please.

156
00:16:16,467 --> 00:16:18,264
You know him, don't you?

157
00:16:18,336 --> 00:16:20,396
Che Guevara.
Never heard of him?

158
00:16:23,242 --> 00:16:25,039
Remember to give her this.

