444
00:42:23,061 --> 00:42:25,120
You, Chirom, take his place.

445
00:42:26,297 --> 00:42:28,663
C'mon gentlemen, move.

446
00:42:42,380 --> 00:42:45,645
Pisani, come over here.

447
00:42:46,150 --> 00:42:48,641
