465
00:45:44,262 --> 00:45:45,922
Your superior.

466
00:45:46,897 --> 00:45:48,660
Be smart.

467
00:45:49,166 --> 00:45:51,225
The name and we'll stop.

468
00:45:53,570 --> 00:45:55,435
Open your hands.

469
00:46:08,218 --> 00:46:11,449
