501
00:48:27,324 --> 00:48:29,588
The kids of the
night of the pencils.

502
00:48:30,226 --> 00:48:31,591
What?

503
00:48:32,028 --> 00:48:33,824
The soldiers call it like that.

504
00:48:33,896 --> 00:48:37,059
The night they
grabbed the students.

505
00:48:37,533 --> 00:48:40,661
Who? Claudia Falcone?
Horacio Ungaro?

506
00:48:40,736 --> 00:48:42,499
Panchito Lopez Muntaner?

507
00:48:42,604 --> 00:48:45,402
