867
01:22:47,041 --> 01:22:50,203
Claudia, will you pray with me?

868
01:22:51,678 --> 01:22:53,669
- Will it help you?
- Yes.

869
01:22:54,581 --> 01:22:56,014
All right.

870
01:22:56,116 --> 01:22:57,811
<i>Why pray?</i>

871
