876
01:23:09,262 --> 01:23:11,230
Don't argue.

877
01:23:12,165 --> 01:23:13,996
Let's sing something together.

878
01:23:14,868 --> 01:23:16,461
Come on, Claudia.

879
01:23:17,637 --> 01:23:19,264
